<p>Adobe Photoshop leads in comprehensive editing capabilities, while alternatives like Capture One Pro and Affinity Photo offer efficient batch editing and professional features. Compression tools like Compress Now, and JPEG Optimizer reduce file sizes without sacrificing quality, essential for improving website load times.</p>
