<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>By integrating these tools and strategies, website owners can significantly improve their site's visual content, optimizing images for both aesthetics and performance.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Final Thoughts</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

